quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,55,"(Ẹ rántí) nígbà tí ẹ wí pé: “Mūsā, a ò níí gbàgbọ́ nínú rẹ àfi kí á rí Allāhu ní ojúkojú.” Nítorí náà, iná láti ojú sánmọ̀ gba yín mú, ẹ sì ń wò bọ̀ọ̀."
  2,56,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A ji yín dìde lẹ́yìn ikú yín, nítorí kí ẹ lè dúpẹ́ (fún Allāhu).1"
  2,57,"A tún fi ẹ̀ṣújò ṣe ibòji fún yín. A sì tún sọ (ohun mímu) mọnnuàti (ohun jíjẹ) salwā2 kalẹ̀ fún yín. Ẹ jẹ nínú àwọn n̄ǹkan dáadáa tí A pèsè fún yín. Wọn kò sì ṣàbòsí sí Wa, ṣùgbọ́n ẹ̀mí ara wọn ni wọ́n ń ṣàbòsí sí. {1}",footnotes:1:Adùn rẹ̀ dà bí adùn oyin.